  "text": "Total RNA was extracted from the frozen liver and ATs samples. RNA was analysed by realtime PCR as described previously [CITATION_1] in the presence of specific primer pairs (S3 Table) with data normalized relatively to Gusb (beta-glucuronidase, for liver) or Hprt (hypoxanthine ribosyl transferase, for AT) mRNA expression levels.",
